                </div><div id='funcionalidades' class='avia-section header_color avia-section-default avia-no-border-styling  avia-bg-style-scroll  avia-builder-el-43  el_after_av_section  el_before_av_section   container_wrap fullsize' style='background-color: #333333;  '>
                    <div class='av-section-color-overlay-wrap'>
                        <a href='#next-section' title='' class='scroll-down-link  av-custom-scroll-down-color' style='color: #ffffff;' aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'></a><div class='container'>
                            <div class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'>
                                <div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-152'>
                                    <div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>
                                        <div style='padding-bottom:0px; font-size:30px;' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h3  blockquote modern-quote modern-centered  avia-builder-el-44  el_before_av_hr  avia-builder-el-first  av-inherit-size '><h3 class='av-special-heading-tag ' itemprop="headline">Funcionalidades destacadas</h3><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border'></div></div></div>
                                        <div style=' margin-top:15px; margin-bottom:0px;' class='hr hr-custom hr-center hr-icon-no   avia-builder-el-45  el_after_av_heading  el_before_av_one_third '><span class='hr-inner  inner-border-av-border-fat' style=' width:50px; border-color:#ffffff;'><span class='hr-inner-style'></span></span></div>
                                        <div class='flex_column_table av-equal-height-column-flextable -flextable'>
                                            <div class="flex_column av_one_third  av-animated-generic bottom-to-top  flex_column_table_cell av-equal-height-column av-align-top first  avia-builder-el-46  el_after_av_hr  el_before_av_one_third  " style='border-radius:0px; '>
                                                <div class='avia-image-container  av-styling-no-styling av-hover-grow noHover  av-overlay-hover-deactivate   avia-builder-el-47  el_before_av_heading  avia-builder-el-first  avia-align-center ' itemprop="image" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"><div class='avia-image-container-inner'><div class='avia-image-overlay-wrap'><div class='av-image-caption-overlay'><div class='av-caption-image-overlay-bg' style='opacity:0.4; background-color:#004b89; '></div><div class='av-image-caption-overlay-position'><div class='av-image-caption-overlay-center' style='color:#ffffff; '></div></div></div><picture><source media='(max-width: 768px)' srcset='/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tracking-de-barriles-1200x423-sm.webp' type='image/webp' width='343' height='121' /><img loading='lazy' decoding='async' class='avia_image' src='/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tracking-de-barriles-1200x423.webp' alt='Sistema de tracking y trazabilidad de barriles de cerveza con código QR' title='Tracking de barriles' height="423" width="1200" itemprop="thumbnailUrl" /></picture></div></div></div>
                                                <div style='padding-bottom:0px; color:#0087cf;font-size:20px;' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h3 custom-color-heading blockquote modern-quote modern-centered  avia-builder-el-48  el_after_av_image  el_before_av_font_icon  encabezados_funcionalidades av-inherit-size '><h3 class='av-special-heading-tag ' itemprop="headline">Trazabilidad <span style="font-family: arial;">&#038;</span> Tracking de barriles</h3><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' style='border-color:#0087cf'></div></div></div>
                                                <span class="av_font_icon avia_animate_when_visible avia-icon-animate  av-icon-style-  avia-icon-pos-center " style="color:#ffffff; border-color:#ffffff;"><span class='av-icon-char' style='font-size:35px;line-height:35px;' aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'></span></span>
                                                <section class="av_textblock_section " itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork">
                                                    <div class='avia_textblock  av_inherit_color ' style='color:#ffffff; ' itemprop="text">
                                                        <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">La trazabilidad es clave para el negocio. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Te proporcionamos información detallada del proceso de elaboración de tus productos hasta su comercialización. A través de información precisa y de fácil lectura que se despliega mediante gráficos e informes. </span></p>
                                                        <ul>
                                                            <li style="text-align: justify;"><b>Tracking de barriles</b>: código barras/QR, remitos con nro de barril, barriles adeudados, rotación de barriles.</li>
                                                            <li style="text-align: justify;"><b>Tracking activos</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: código barras/QR para activos como heladeras/neveras, choperas, canillas, tap handles, etc.</span></li>
                                                        </ul>
                                                    </div>
                                                </section>
                                            </div><div class='av-flex-placeholder'></div><div class="flex_column av_one_third  av-animated-generic bottom-to-top  flex_column_table_cell av-equal-height-column av-align-top av-zero-column-padding   avia-builder-el-51  el_after_av_one_third  el_before_av_one_third  " style='border-radius:0px; '>
                                                <div class='avia-image-container  av-styling-no-styling av-hover-grow noHover  av-overlay-hover-deactivate   avia-builder-el-52  el_before_av_heading  avia-builder-el-first  avia-align-center ' itemprop="image" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"><div class='avia-image-container-inner'><div class='avia-image-overlay-wrap'><div class='av-image-caption-overlay'><div class='av-caption-image-overlay-bg' style='opacity:0.4; background-color:#004b89; '></div><div class='av-image-caption-overlay-position'><div class='av-image-caption-overlay-center' style='color:#ffffff; '></div></div></div><picture><source media='(max-width: 768px)' srcset='/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/envasado-cerveza-1200x423-sm.webp' type='image/webp' width='343' height='121' /><img loading='lazy' decoding='async' class='avia_image' src='/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/envasado-cerveza-1200x423.webp' alt='Módulo de envasado de cerveza artesanal en latas, botellas y barriles' title='envasado-cerveza' height="423" width="1200" itemprop="thumbnailUrl" /></picture></div></div></div>
                                                <div style='padding-bottom:0px; color:#0087cf;font-size:20px;' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h3 custom-color-heading blockquote modern-quote modern-centered  avia-builder-el-53  el_after_av_image  el_before_av_font_icon  encabezados_funcionalidades av-inherit-size '><h3 class='av-special-heading-tag ' itemprop="headline">Envasado</h3><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' style='border-color:#0087cf'></div></div></div>
                                                <span class="av_font_icon avia_animate_when_visible avia-icon-animate  av-icon-style-  avia-icon-pos-center " style="color:#ffffff; border-color:#ffffff;"><span class='av-icon-char' style='font-size:35px;line-height:35px;' aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'></span></span>
                                                <section class="av_textblock_section " itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork">
                                                    <div class='avia_textblock  av_inherit_color ' style='color:#ffffff; ' itemprop="text">
                                                        <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Planifica el destino de tu producto desde la materia prima y elaboración hasta el consumidor final sin perder la trazabilidad.</span></p>
                                                        <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">A través de Gestión Cervecera elige el envasado para tu producto:</span></p>
                                                        <ul>
                                                            <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Latas</strong></span></li>
                                                            <li style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Botellas</strong></li>
                                                            <li style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Packs:</strong> simples o packs de latas/botellas con productos combinados para la venta. Los mix-pack tienen su propio nro. de lote y fecha de vencimiento con lo cual se mantiene la trazabilidad del producto.</li>
                                                        </ul>
                                                    </div>
                                                </section>
                                            </div><div class='av-flex-placeholder'></div><div class="flex_column av_one_third  av-animated-generic bottom-to-top  flex_column_table_cell av-equal-height-column av-align-top av-zero-column-padding   avia-builder-el-56  el_after_av_one_third  el_before_av_one_fourth  " style='border-radius:0px; '>
                                                <div class='avia-image-container  av-styling-no-styling av-hover-grow noHover  av-overlay-hover-deactivate   avia-builder-el-57  el_before_av_heading  avia-builder-el-first  avia-align-center ' itemprop="image" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"><div class='avia-image-container-inner'><div class='avia-image-overlay-wrap'><div class='av-image-caption-overlay'><div class='av-caption-image-overlay-bg' style='opacity:0.4; background-color:#004b89; '></div><div class='av-image-caption-overlay-position'><div class='av-image-caption-overlay-center' style='color:#ffffff; '></div></div></div><picture><source media='(max-width: 768px)' srcset='/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Distribuidores-Bares-Franquicias-1200x423-sm.webp' type='image/webp' width='343' height='121' /><img loading='lazy' decoding='async' class='avia_image' src='/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Distribuidores-Bares-Franquicias-1200x423.webp' alt='Software de gestión para distribuidoras de cerveza, bares y franquicias' title='Distribuidores-Bares-Franquicias' height="423" width="1200" itemprop="thumbnailUrl" /></picture></div></div></div>
                                                <div style='padding-bottom:0px; color:#0087cf;font-size:20px;' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h3 custom-color-heading blockquote modern-quote modern-centered  avia-builder-el-58  el_after_av_image  el_before_av_font_icon  encabezados_funcionalidades av-inherit-size '><h3 class='av-special-heading-tag ' itemprop="headline">Distribuidoras &#8211; Bares &#8211; Franquicias</h3><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' style='border-color:#0087cf'></div></div></div>
                                                <span class="av_font_icon avia_animate_when_visible avia-icon-animate  av-icon-style-  avia-icon-pos-center " style="color:#ffffff; border-color:#ffffff;"><span class='av-icon-char' style='font-size:35px;line-height:35px;' aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'></span></span>
                                                <section class="av_textblock_section " itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork">
                                                    <div class='avia_textblock  av_inherit_color ' style='color:#ffffff; ' itemprop="text">
                                                        <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Facilitamos la comercialización de tu producto. Ofrecemos soporte e integración para todo el ecosistema.</span></p>
                                                        <ul>
                                                            <li style="text-align: justify;"><b>Ventas a través de distribuidoras</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: bloqueo de stock, compras de barriles, devolución de barriles a proveedor, comisiones por venta/cobranza</span></li>
                                                            <li style="text-align: justify;"><b>Bares/franquicias</b>: pedidos a través del sitio, cta. cte., devolución de barriles vacíos con remito</li>
                                                        </ul>
                                                    </div>
                                                </section>
                                            </div>
                                        </div><!--close column table wrapper. Autoclose: 1 --><div class='flex_column_table av-equal-height-column-flextable -flextable'>
                                            <div class="flex_column av_one_fourth  av-animated-generic bottom-to-top  flex_column_table_cell av-equal-height-column av-align-top av-zero-column-padding first  avia-builder-el-61  el_after_av_one_third  el_before_av_one_fourth  column-top-margin" style='border-radius:0px; '>
                                                <div class='avia-image-container  av-styling-no-styling av-hover-grow noHover  av-overlay-hover-deactivate   avia-builder-el-62  el_before_av_heading  avia-builder-el-first  avia-align-center ' itemprop="image" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"><div class='avia-image-container-inner'><div class='avia-image-overlay-wrap'><div class='av-image-caption-overlay'><div class='av-caption-image-overlay-bg' style='opacity:0.4; background-color:#004b89; '></div><div class='av-image-caption-overlay-position'><div class='av-image-caption-overlay-center' style='color:#ffffff; '></div></div></div><picture><source media='(max-width: 768px)' srcset='/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ecommerce-1-845x321-sm.webp' type='image/webp' width='239' height='91' /><img loading='lazy' decoding='async' class='avia_image' src='/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ecommerce-1-845x321.webp' alt='Integración e-commerce para venta online de cerveza artesanal' title='ecommerce' height="321" width="845" itemprop="thumbnailUrl" /></picture></div></div></div>
                                                <div style='padding-bottom:0px; color:#0087cf;font-size:20px;' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h3 custom-color-heading blockquote modern-quote modern-centered  avia-builder-el-63  el_after_av_image  el_before_av_font_icon  encabezados_funcionalidades av-inherit-size '><h3 class='av-special-heading-tag ' itemprop="headline">Ventas online &#8211; eCommerce</h3><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' style='border-color:#0087cf'></div></div></div>
                                                <span class="av_font_icon avia_animate_when_visible avia-icon-animate  av-icon-style-  avia-icon-pos-center " style="color:#ffffff; border-color:#ffffff;"><span class='av-icon-char' style='font-size:35px;line-height:35px;' aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'></span></span>
                                                <section class="av_textblock_section " itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork">
                                                    <div class='avia_textblock  av_inherit_color ' style='color:#ffffff; ' itemprop="text">
                                                        <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Nos integramos con canales de venta online, lo que permite que los pedidos que recibas online pasan a Gestión Cervecera automáticamente para que los puedas gestionar y entregar en tiempo y forma.</span></p>
                                                    </div>
                                                </section>
                                            </div><div class='av-flex-placeholder'></div><div class="flex_column av_one_fourth  av-animated-generic bottom-to-top  flex_column_table_cell av-equal-height-column av-align-top av-zero-column-padding   avia-builder-el-66  el_after_av_one_fourth  el_before_av_one_fourth  column-top-margin" style='border-radius:0px; '>
                                                <div class='avia-image-container  av-styling-no-styling av-hover-grow noHover  av-overlay-hover-deactivate   avia-builder-el-67  el_before_av_heading  avia-builder-el-first  avia-align-center ' itemprop="image" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"><div class='avia-image-container-inner'><div class='avia-image-overlay-wrap'><div class='av-image-caption-overlay'><div class='av-caption-image-overlay-bg' style='opacity:0.4; background-color:#004b89; '></div><div class='av-image-caption-overlay-position'><div class='av-image-caption-overlay-center' style='color:#ffffff; '></div></div></div><picture><source media='(max-width: 768px)' srcset='/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/facturacion-electronica-845x321-sm.webp' type='image/webp' width='239' height='91' /><img loading='lazy' decoding='async' class='avia_image' src='/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/facturacion-electronica-845x321.webp' alt='Módulo de facturación electrónica para cervecerías de Latinoamérica' title='facturacion electronica' height="321" width="845" itemprop="thumbnailUrl" /></picture></div></div></div>
                                                <div style='padding-bottom:0px; color:#0087cf;font-size:20px;' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h3 custom-color-heading blockquote modern-quote modern-centered  avia-builder-el-68  el_after_av_image  el_before_av_font_icon  encabezados_funcionalidades av-inherit-size '><h3 class='av-special-heading-tag ' itemprop="headline">Facturación electrónica</h3><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' style='border-color:#0087cf'></div></div></div>
                                                <span class="av_font_icon avia_animate_when_visible avia-icon-animate  av-icon-style-  avia-icon-pos-center " style="color:#ffffff; border-color:#ffffff;"><span class='av-icon-char' style='font-size:35px;line-height:35px;' aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'></span></span>
                                                <section class="av_textblock_section " itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork">
                                                    <div class='avia_textblock  av_inherit_color ' style='color:#ffffff; ' itemprop="text">
                                                        <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Tenemos partners con quienes nos integramos para la facturación electrónica en cada país, lo cual te permite hacer facturas y notas de crédito directamente desde Gestión Cervecera y que las mismas contemplen toda la legislación local vigente.</span></p>
                                                    </div>
